@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "History";
    Layout = "~/Views/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<!-- History Section -->
<div class="container py-4">
    <div class="row align-items-center g-5">
        <!-- Text Section -->
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-7">
            <h1 class="fw-bold text-primary mb-3" style="font-size:2rem;">Our History</h1>
            <p class="text-dark">
                SKR International School, established in 2018 by <strong>Mrs. Anupam Kumari</strong>, began with a vision to redefine education through compassion, innovation, and excellence. What started as a modest institution has grown into a vibrant center of learning that nurtures young minds to become responsible global citizens.
            </p>
            <p class="text-dark">
                From its inception, SKR International School has embraced a holistic approach to education — blending academic rigor with creativity, ethics, and emotional intelligence. The school’s foundation rests on the belief that every child deserves an environment that encourages curiosity, confidence, and character.
            </p>
            <p class="text-dark">
                Over the years, the institution has expanded its infrastructure, introduced advanced learning technologies, and built a team of dedicated educators who share the founder’s vision. Today, SKR International School stands as a beacon of quality education, inspiring generations to dream big and achieve with integrity.
            </p>
            <p class="text-dark">
                The journey continues — guided by values, strengthened by achievements, and driven by the unwavering commitment to shape the leaders of tomorrow.
            </p>
        </div>

        
    </div>
</div>

